  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The first and the second, I don't think it to be more than three minutes to be out of the camp from the first and the second wire.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The only thing that's left is that tank, anti-tank, horses, and the net that easily get caught in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The rain helped the miracle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's like the Jews in the-- in the Sinai desert when manna rained from the-- from the sky and how [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Moshe ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Rabbani ?] got the water from that rock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And you wouldn't be surprised that I thought of those things as not religious as I am.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "These are those miracles that I, that you only can read in the Bible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I neglected to mention, as I was running into the barrack before I'm tracking back now, I said to myself-- and I know these are the words that I felt, 'I knew,' quote, unquote, that's the end of the line.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I said to myself, So in God's name, so may be.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I hope it doesn't hurt, I hope it's quick and over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But that's why that hasn't happened to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now I'm out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I had about three hundred yards to the end of the-- to-- to-- to get to the-- to the last obstacle.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And miraculously, all I needed to do was crawl under it and lift it up with my back to make sure that no body parts get caught in it-- in it, and that took me less than a minute.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It didn't take me more than four minutes to get out of this camp, when one wouldn't think it could be done.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
